name: Beautiful red wool felt hat with feather spray
description: This is a beautiful dressy hat made by Plaza Suites, that can be worn dressed up or down.  It is so easy to wear and beautifully accents any outfit!!  Fits up to a size 23!

name: Lord & Taylor white dress hat
description: This beautiful clean hat by Lord & Taylor is perfect for any dressy occasion!

name: Beautiful red vintage cap with feather
description: This lovely red feathered cap has a simple style to it.  It is fur felt, a small piece of the white feather is missing/damaged, but is in otherwise great condition.

name: Beautiful vintage chocolate wool rounded fedora
description: This is an unusually shaped brown fedora.  It has a round crown with a unusual shaped brim.  This is a fantastic addition to any hat collection.

name: Slanted vintage black wool fedora
description: This funky fedora has a slanted crown, with a wide grossgrain ribbon.  Plain and simple!

name: Beauiful black vintage beaver felt with feathered front
description: Beautiful warm beaver felt, adorned beautifully at the front of crown with a layer of feathers!  A classic winter hat ready for those fine winter coats!

name: Vintage satin rust colored flapper hat with feather spray
description: This is a one of a kind flapper style, dated back to the 40's.  This hat has such a stylish look that I will greatly complement any outfit that is grand enough to handle it.

name: Beautiful vintage feather headband by Traci Vest
description: Fabulous vintage headband by Traci Vest in excellent condition.  Blends in beautifully with hair!!  Leather holder!

name: Beautiful vintage wool beige boater
description: This is a lovely wool boater style hat in a light beige color.  It has a beautfiful emblem and a wide long three strand ribbon that adds a wonderful flare to this topper.

name: Vintage fine woven straw with feathers and bird claw
description:
This love navy blue cap has a bird claw accented with feathers, due to use, it does have a missing feather.

In last picture, other hats and hat box not included

name: Cute vintage maroon/burgunday wool felt hat
description: This is a lovely hat is an awesome design.  You have to have attitude to cock this one on your crown!!

name: Vintage wool blue tri colored half hat cap with bakelite and feather
description: This is a lovely cap/half hat i three shades of blue in a lovely fur felt with a stunning bakelite decorative piece with feather.  For lovers of blue!!

name: Vintage chocolate fedora w/animal print band
description: This lovely fedora with its faux fur animal print wide band with buckle is certainly a show stopper!  Again, they just don't make them like this anymore!!  A nice felt hat!

name: Vintage cone shape slant burnt orange fedora
description: This is certainly a classic cone shaped fedora!!  You don't find many that have this spectacular design anymore.  This is a wool fedora style with wide ribbon band.  This is awesome casual or dressy!!

name: Arturochiang Silver open toed slingbacks size 7
description: This is a pair lovely of silver lightly used sandals, new lifts have been added.

name: Dainty yellow half hat
description: Just a simple yellow hat with flowerettes at the front, woven of a synthetic material, very easy to wear.

name: Amish Style
description: This hat is more than likely a reproduction due to its impeccable condition; made of a black cotton like material.

name: Straw black wide brim
description: This hat is a 1940's wide brim, has a gross grain ribbon and an embroidered folded front brim.   This hat is in very good condition

name: Lime Green woven cap by Adolfo II
description: This hat is a beautiful shade of green.  It has a couple of spots on two of the bows, from aged glue, shown in pics.  Price right!

name: Mr. John Cloche
description: This loosely woven hat is a Mr. John  Classic/Lord and Taylor is black with a velour bow.  A very comfortable fit coming down on the head for that cloche style.

name: Multi colored cap
description: This hat is layered and has shades of mint green, light blue and gold threading on cream.  A side bow blends in and is hardly noticeable in the pictures.

name: Sheer pink rosette bandeau
description: This lovely bouquet of pink flowerettes set to a band is so soft and feminine with its sheer netting.

name: Off white cloche style
description: This is the simplest of hat designs to wear!  This off white cloche styled hat works with any outfit.  Shows some sign of wear on the bow front.

name: Dobbs original man's hat
description: This is an older Dobbs original!  Has some wear to the lining, but does not take away from the hat.

name: Navy blue by Conrad Chandler
description: This is an unusual hat by Conrad Chandler, made of strips of curly synthetic material.  Sure to make a statement!

name: vintage Black and off white fine woven straw
description: Dainty and simply elegant black and off white hat with nice netting, comes with original hatpin.  Straw like material in very good condition!

name: Navy blue stripe by First Issue
description: A lovely cream straw type material with navy blue stripes by First Issue.  Nice wide brim that can be adjusted and worn the way you like!

name: Pink knit cap with petals
description: This lovely pink knit cap is loaded with pale pink petals!

name: Red velour bandeau with feather trim
description: Lovely red velour bandeau styled hat, with fine red feather accentuated with netting.

name: Rhinestone choker
description: A lovely rhinestone choker, with glamour written all over it!!  Perfect for any after 5 event, knock em dead!!

name: Weiss Rhinestone Necklace
description:
Rhinestones are a girls best friend when Diamonds are not available.  

This Weiss rhinestone necklace is stamped, and shining from 
A to Z!!  Nothing but clarity in these stones, another stunning piece as only Weiss can do it!!

name: Cap of three woven shades
description: This hat is woven of three shades including black, tan and beige.  A striking combination that is also complemented with a grossgrain band and bow with a shiny patent running through its center.  THis hat is slouched on the right side.

name: Straw bubble toque
description: Cute bubble style, with a slight slouch on the right side, mildly pleated around crown, small band and a bow.  Absolutely cool!!

name: Plush off white faux fur
description: This is one of the nicest faux furs I've come across, (there's a black one too)!  This one is quite stylish and has the shades of a real fur. Looks amazing!

name: Cocoa brown woven hat with patent bow
description: This lovely hat comes loaded with velour trim on the brim and a patent bow and band to set it all off.

name: Black wool cap
description: This exciting black wool cap has an intersting design that's made to impress.  An excellent fit, and comfortable design make this hat a winner.  It has a folded top, a slouched side and the front with a the look of a man's applejack hat.  Wool ribbon forms a bow on the side.  Too cool!!

name: Pretty shade of red
description: This very feminine hat is a light shade of red, loaded with flower petals at its front, tapering on the right side for a serious look.

name: Nice animal print in suede
description: One of my favorite animal print styles, this is a nice suede, true to color to match your favorite animal print hand bag, belt or shoes!!  This is a a soft stylish hat that can also be worn slouched. The band and bow are a patent leather material.

name: Navy blue wide brim Liz Clairborne
description: The material of the hat is feels and looks like corduroy, very soft in excellent condition.  This is a great winter hat with wide brim, a nice shade of navy blue.

name: Black Velour and Satin
description:
This unusually styled hat by Lisette is a reproduction.  It has a velour cap that fits the head securely, with a full backdrop in satiny black.  There is a velour bow that sits on the top of the velour cap.

The back can be pinned up, with a vintage hat pin of course, or you can create a design all your own with this one!!

name: Black tapered wide brim
description: This lovely wide brim is tapered in the back and has a small bow which complements its sleek design!

name: Lilly Dachette Animal Print
description: This wide brim is absolutely a bold statement made by famous milliner Lilly Dachette!  The brim can be turned up or worn down.  This hat does come down further on the crown of the head, if you are looking for that covered eye look!!

name: Black and bold
description:
This hat is simply beautiful and in excellent condition.  This is a simple but classic design.  The gems are absolutely perfect.

Hat will best fit size 21 1/2.

name: Vintage rhinestone necklace
description: Lovely rhinestones set in rhodium, the metal does not turn color, the next best thing to diamonds!!

name: Off white fur felt
description: A very unusual design in off white fur felt, a criss cross design that sits very comfortably on the crown of your head.

name: Brown Half hat
description: This wool felt chocolate brown hat has two small beige roses with rhinestones encircling their stems.

name: Soft Yellow Cloche
description: This vintage hat is made of a soft cotton, and is a soft yellow color.  Simple, yet adorable!

name: Navy blue boater
description: A simple navy blue boater with lovely long ribbon made of straw!

name: Fur felt of mustard and forest green
description: This is a vivid color combination of mustard and forest/olive green, a simple upturned brim with small bow.  Small moth hole pictured on rear of hat, not noticeable when wearing.

name: Turquoise Normand Duran
description: A simple curved brim and lovey bow make this hat a classic look!

name: Half by hat by Lucilie Parisi
description: Adorable half hat, copper color beads make a nice decoration to the front of hat, fine brown stripes are complemented by silver colored base.  Priced low due to spot of damage, does not take away from beauty of this hat!

name: Baby blue pillbox
description: Simple baby blue pillbox in a woven material.

name: Plush black faux fur
description: It's beginning to feel like fall in some places, and you know what's next.  Time to get out the fashionable warm gear.  This lovely black faux fur is plush and warm!!

name: Turquoisey green tam knitted with sequins
description: This is a nice knitted tam in deep green turqoisey color with circular sequins.

name: Black cone shaped sequined knit
description: This hat is knitted in large loops with pretty circular sequins sprinkled about its unusual cone shape.

name: Winter white pointed brim
description: This is a nice suede type material in white.  Has an interior cap that holds the hat to the crown of your head.  There is some spotting to the interior, see pics.

name: Sequined ivory scull cap
description: This is a lovely "Made in Italy" sequined scull cap, on a knit base.

name: White flowers
description: This is a tall pillbox style, not made to come down far on the head, but a tall sitting hat.  Makes a big statement.  Has some yellow spots on a couple of the brim flowers petals.  Does not take away from the beauty of this hat!!

name: Navy blue tall pillbox
description: This is a nice dark navy blue pillbox with velour bow and trim.

name: Off white woven pillbox
description: This is a tall pillbox with long ribbon to accentuate its length.  A clean classic look.

name: Olive green pillbox
description: This is a simply designed olive green pillbox with a ribbon accentuated with a gold band.

name: Chocolate brown and pearls
description: A very simply designed half hat made of chocolate brown velour with a pearl decorated front.

name: Classic Cloche
description: The unmistakeable style of a cloche, one of my favorite classic designs.  Nothing frames the face like the cloche.  The material is a soft velour material, with a sewn design on the crown.

name: Lovely straw wide brim w/flowers
description: This straw wide brim hat is such a nicely made hat, its color is rich and deep.  Flowers are in excellent condition and vibrantly colored.  Wears very well!!

name: Navy blue pillbox in sheer layers
description: This navy blue pillbox is adorable with sheer layers and netting to cover!

name: Brand new Sam and Libby shoes
description: These are a nice pair of Sam and Libby pointed toe shoes in black, size 8 1/2.

name: Luciano Padovan Orange red sling backs size
description: This pair of reddish sling backs is used and has some minor wear at the toe.  But considering its style and the designer, they certainly have a lot more to give!

name: Lovely lavender wide brim
description: This hat is so feminine with its sheer covered crown, a very light lavender shade with a large group of purple flowers!!

name: Kenneth Cole Mules
description: This pair of Kenneth Cole shoes are in very good condition, size 8.

name: Navy blue with white brim
description: This hat is like new with a lovely shine navy straw with white brim!  Side buttons and small red bows accentuate this simple hat by Bellini!

name: Tri colored wide brim
description:
Brim is a light beige and crown is off white and of course the orange ribbon!  There is evidence of a previous feather, which is now missing.  I think I'll add some, and then take more pictures!!

This hat still has tag holders on it, brand new.  Interior band shows that it has been tried on a few times.  Also some minor aging spots on interior, see pics.

name: Bold and beautiful
description: This hat is boldly colored, not for the faint hearted!!

name: Gray fedora
description: This is a ladies fedora, sorry guys.  Very attractive with ribbon and original hat pin!

name: Chocolatey pillbox
description: Beautiful hat by the well know "Lilly Dache," one of the greatest if not the greatest in vintage hats!!

name: Turquoise with petals
description: An adorable stylish half hat.  Embellished with a large group of petals

name: Looks like a ladybug
description: Red straw like material, with black beads!  Black ribbon and small sidebow.

name: Ivory with shimmer
description: A different style, stretchy with some shimmer!  Always a need for this color in church services!

name: Pretty in Pink
description: A Lovely pink straw with large pink rose,very feminine and attractive!

name: Simply navy
description:
This one reminds me of those well dressed ladies who didn't leave home without their hats!  
 
A very simple style!

name: Shiny and black pillbox
description: This small pillbox sits atop the head, cocked of course, has two combs to hold securely in place.  Gotta have spunk to wear this one!  Beautiful and shiny...

name: Black Nina Comfort
description: Nice pair of shoes by Nina, size 8B.  Barely worn condition.

name: Pink half hat with crystal deco
description: This is a nice pink felt half hat with long bow shape in front detailed with crystals.

name: Black felt with shiny decor
description: This is a gorgeous black felt cap like hat with top of brim decorated in shiny button like detailing.

name: Wide brim tan and white straw
description:
Introducing this lovely wide brim, with tan and white woven straw!  MUST have attitude to work this HAT!

Sits atop the head and cocked!

name: Hat by Doris
description: This is a stunning wide brim with black velour crown, and brim made of knitted tan, white and black.  Sits atop the head, does not pull down.  You MUST have the ability to work this HAT!!!

name: Lovely off-white straw
description: This is a nice off white straw hat with layers of tulle on the brim.

name: Off white with rhinestones
description: This hat is adorable with its glittering jewels.  Simple but elegant

name: Small brown pillbox
description: This chocolate brown pillbox style hat that is held in place with two attached combs.

name: Small and dainty
description: This hat is of a synthetic woven material, dark blue and tan.  It sits on top of the head and is held in place with an elastic.

name: Lovely in purple
description: This is lovely straw hat in a lavender body with a large purple flower for decoration.

name: Black w/rhinestones
description: This is lovely black hat with two very large rhinestones that are simply glowing.

name: black patent w/rose
description: This is a lovely black patent hat with straw like brim, and has a lovely red and pink rose fits size 22.

name: Purple strappy nine west size 8B
description: These are used dress shoes in good condition, made by Nine West.  The color show is true, a nice deep purple.
